@scotttovey That is true. Everyone does mistakes. People are not computers. But I believe this is a probability thing. If I can make a 3 min video without any retakes then I would allow myself to commend myself with a -Good job you're a pro.
Especially after struggling with previous videos. 
People should allow themselves to feel like a pro more often I think. It's a good motivational boost.
